## Geo Search Point Field

A geo point that is resolved from a search key (place name) via geocoding, then rendered on a Leaflet map.

### Usage

```ts
import { CardDef, field, contains } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import GeoSearchPointField from '@cardstack/catalog/fields/geo-search-point/geo-search-point';

export class Example extends CardDef {
  @field location = contains(GeoSearchPointField, {
    configuration: { zoom: 13 },
  });
}
```

See the **Examples** section of this spec for the full set of supported configuration options.
